      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative solver residuals monitored to convergence tolerance <1e-6; nonlinear equilibrium iterations converged to force residual <0.1% of applied load at each increment.",
      "rationale": "Sparse direct solver used for linear steps; Newton-Raphson iterations for nonlinear contact. Force residual norm fell below 0.05% of applied load at every converged increment. No divergence events observed across all 11 model instances. Required Gradation 2 achieved."
