      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties (E, nu, yield strength) sourced from ASTM material certificates for each lot; geometric inputs from calibrated CMM measurements of actual test articles. Input uncertainty quantified.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and Poisson's ratio taken from material certificates for the specific Ti-6Al-4V lot used in fabrication. CMM measurements of 3 representative screws confirmed CAD nominal dimensions within 0.02 mm. Monte Carlo uncertainty propagation on material and geometric inputs performed; combined input uncertainty contribution to QoI uncertainty <4%. Required Gradation 3 achieved."
