      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production-representative hardware. Dimensional inspection of all 11 screws confirmed conformance to drawing tolerances. Power analysis confirmed N=11 provides 80% power to detect 10% QoI difference at alpha=0.05. Required Gradation 3 achieved."
