      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions replicate COU loading environment; multiple load levels or configurations tested; environmental conditions (temperature, humidity) documented and controlled.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under standard ASTM F1717 protocol at a single load configuration (compression-bending at 5 degrees). Only one test condition evaluated; multi-load-level or multi-angle testing not performed. Temperature and humidity logged but not varied. Achieved Gradation 2 against required Gradation 3 — identified gap accepted given MEDIUM model risk and corroborating analytical evidence."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
