      "rationale": "Fixture geometry digitized from laboratory drawings and incorporated into FEA model. Applied displacement rate converted to quasi-static load in model; inertial effects confirmed negligible at 5 mm/min crosshead speed. Constraint locations matched to within 0.5 mm of physical fixture. Required Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
