      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9 for stiffness (1.12), yield force (0.87), and force at 40 mm (1.34). All values below 1.96. Percent differences: stiffness 4.2%, yield force 3.8%, force at 40 mm 6.1% — all below 10% threshold. Required Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
