      "rationale": "The validation experiment uses the same screw design, material lot, and test protocol as the COU. Two independent laboratories performed testing, increasing confidence in experimental reference data. The FEA model evaluated is the same ensemble submitted for regulatory review. Validation activities are directly relevant to the COU. Required Gradation 3 achieved."
