    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3; this gap is accepted on the basis of MEDIUM model risk level, corroborating analytical sensitivity studies, and the availability of multi-laboratory experimental data that partially compensates for the single test condition. Quantitative comparison metrics (E/uval <1.96, percent difference <10%) satisfied for all three QoIs across all FEA ensemble members. The credibility evidence package is sufficient to support regulatory submission.",
